Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(無臉男)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.54,0:00:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日置藩藩士佐佐木一家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.14,0:00:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘遭滅門的血案
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此宣佈裁決
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.31,0:00:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木家當家一正之妻蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊街示眾之後\N再處以磔刑懸首示眾！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…輕鬆多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謹遵裁處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.92,0:01:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(前篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.24,0:01:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清冷的月光照着你徘徊的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話卻說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.40,0:01:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶記那虛偽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻那溫暖的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什麼樣的風景？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.05,0:02:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的下弦月隱臟於雲間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述說着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱着孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又將對月長嘆…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來事情也就告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.25,0:02:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底做了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如妳所見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟妳一樣是囚犯喲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個賣藥的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到一個奇怪的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我的藥一點效也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還硬說我是騙子什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種一昧想靠藥治病的態度\N就令人不快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會沒有效果\N都是因為你信心不足
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有句\N“精神所至金子會開”嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如此反唇相譏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果他就直嚷着要我還錢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還告上衙門
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後就落得這個下場真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…應該是\N“精誠所至金石為開”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要叫人囉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.01,0:03:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不覺得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟把男人跟女人\N關在同一個牢房裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼大驚小怪反正妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被判死罪了不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道得還真清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.26,0:03:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為街頭巷尾都在談妳的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說妳是殺死丈夫以及婆婆等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士全家的惡鬼妻子蝴蝶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們這樣形容我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.25,0:04:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚人呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把四個人吊在梅樹上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，奇怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是怎樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.35,0:04:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？\N怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.15,0:04:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？忘了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了反正謠言總會被加油添醋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題不在於妳怎麼殺死他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是用味噌煮湯或鹽烤\N鯖魚還是鯖魚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂您的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思就是我不覺得\N那是出自一個女人之手喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請別在意，這只是我工作的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既無目擊證詞\N也沒有強而有力的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.20,0:05:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單憑妳自首說“是我幹的”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.17,0:05:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未免太含糊不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這件事並非妳一個人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:06:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得…應該是物怪幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是否…有什麼頭緒呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不完全沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是我一個人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是身上散發出來的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是該有的表情等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說妳根本不像\N明天將被處死之人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說的就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經換上一身白衣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.73,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…那是這裡供給的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撇開服裝不說\N主要是妳的表情喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看起來彷彿變了個人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟平常的蝴蝶小姐完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在胡說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您又不曉得\N平常的我是什麼樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是什麼人，回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個賣藥的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不過現在是囚犯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我，你是怎麼進來這的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話真多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是頭一次\N碰到這樣的物怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人並非什麼可疑之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.76,0:07:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.56,0:07:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！為什麼要阻礙我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.67,0:07:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡是最安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的傢伙你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被纏上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，原以為要揭露其“形”\N得花不少功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然自已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找上門來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其“形”已現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.18,0:08:38.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是物怪的“形”嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要阻礙我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.49,0:08:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這裡是最安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想離開此地的話此地即是牢獄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.60,0:08:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在說什麼啊？\N想留在此地的話此地即是堡壘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想回去那個地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回…去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類更可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.26,0:09:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還是有心地善良的物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到她的話沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.83,0:09:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限之虛空在吾之手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這樣去找“形”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡應該就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵應該暫時不會追來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那些奇奇怪怪的招術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到妳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如那男人所言
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了…\N把妳救出那個牢獄而誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢獄？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牢獄？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！拿酒來，酒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒酒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.08,0:10:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.62,0:10:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶也真是的\N早點拿來不就得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨手笨腳的媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼怪裡怪氣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哥哥你幹嘛娶她？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她老媽苦苦哀求我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是前一個媳婦上吊自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會讓這種女人進門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過娶來煮飯剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要是也能多點情趣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭~你怎麼講這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把如惡鬼般的毒全吐出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許妳會認為我這個物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講這種話很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種觸感…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧那個觸感才讓我能夠熬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次又一次，一次又一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是您救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…還是要回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳必須回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的力量有限\N追兵很快就會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.73,0:12:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再回去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去妳將會成為逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:13:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且妳丈夫一家\N真的會變成是妳殺死的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算回去那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亦或是我不回去都沒什麼差別
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是不回去妳這輩子都會被通緝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許一抓到就會被就地正法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的死法反而輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛剛在牢裡的男人嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.60,0:13:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個男人\N讓妳有這種想法的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自已不想回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.69,0:13:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳願意跟我在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可是您…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.63,0:13:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確，我並非人類
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是正如妳所看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平常的模樣\N跟人類並無兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我無法摘下這個面具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要我做什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會想辦法養活妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳當我的妻子吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這種人也可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌棄我這帶罪之身嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是要妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這意思是妳答應囉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太，太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.97,0:14:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，那我們來慶祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶，我們一起展開新的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.03,0:15:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位~這是我的妻子喔~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.81,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧，是蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~真有一套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有辦法娶蝴蝶小姐為妻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.35,0:15:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕，好羡慕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀可喜可賀…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀可喜可賀…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群亂來的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們好好玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他們一直在妳身邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.43,0:15:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是妳沒發現而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.74,0:15:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一直守護着妳\N好羡慕，好羡慕哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.54,0:15:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人總是很健忘的\N可喜可賀…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記曾經邂逅多少事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記自已被多少人圍繞着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過之後…就不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將成為妳活着的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高砂呀高砂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀，可喜可賀呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來我們就結為連理了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今以後我們就夫妻同心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.32,0:16:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身已將她調教得\N不管何時都不會令家門蒙羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後還請您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後務必請您多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.04,0:16:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，母親大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼，這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出嫁…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來\N我就無愧於梅澤家的代代祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，妳也快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.44,0:17:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好拜託人家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳天生就是個美人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑這個臉蛋再學點技藝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是出身貧寒的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能嫁入大戶人家的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~好孩子，真是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！別讓她看這些！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀可喜可賀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你讓我看了一齣好戲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得很開心喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那個面具…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面具是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.31,0:18:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“面”這個字代表着外表
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂人類的臉\N不過是表現於外的形罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我承認這個面具\N就是我的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼這個面容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將成為我的外表
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，臉又變了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的真面目究竟是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.11,0:19:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易…抓住的新人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩塌了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種虛偽的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.68,0:20:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是物怪為了欺騙妳而安排的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.79,0:20:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為他是來救我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺騙的背後必然隱臟着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還特地戴上面具…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.90,0:20:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精心安排這齣戲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是隱瞞了什麼吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.07,0:20:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記自已面貌的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:20:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現出“形”來！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待續)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法笑得開懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能將那些無可取代的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.46,0:21:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜並活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.97,0:21:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛開在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨風緩緩飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不見的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子\N將是我此生無可比喻的珍愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.12,0:22:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋臟於心中的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便存在於相同之時空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或目睹相同之景物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.72,0:22:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存於你我內心之物\N亦絕非相同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.53,0:22:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我內心深處的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.20,0:22:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(無臉男)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.56,0:23:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(物怪)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清冷的月光照着你徘徊的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.84,0:23:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話卻說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.75,0:23:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶記那虛偽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻那溫暖的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.46,0:24:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什麼樣的風景？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的下弦月隱臟於雲間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.14,0:24:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.18,0:24:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述說着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.25,0:24:15.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱着孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又將對月長嘆…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.62,0:24:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(後篇)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.50,0:24:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈能如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.11,0:24:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你不願現出原形…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.14,0:24:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.25,0:24:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.55,0:24:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.42,0:24:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.82,0:24:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安份一下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.69,0:24:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.27,0:25:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.47,0:25:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.64,0:25:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼剛剛的戲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.48,0:25:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續演下去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.12,0:25:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪的“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.02,0:25:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是基於人的淵源跟因果形成的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.33,0:25:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當妖怪感應到人類的感情或執念
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.86,0:25:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪就會變成物怪\N對了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.13,0:25:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說過您是來斬除物怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.17,0:25:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果現在就能斬除的話\N我也是十分樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.24,0:25:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是物怪的真與理…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.88,0:25:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有若缺少形的話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.35,0:25:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔劍是無法拔出的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.86,0:26:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.09,0:26:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻煩啊！物怪這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.76,0:26:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真”乃事情的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.40,0:26:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”乃心的樣貌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.47,0:26:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若物怪不現出他的“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.11,0:26:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我只得請妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.51,0:26:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細道出真與理
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.95,0:26:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.39,0:26:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.06,0:26:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…一生？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.70,0:26:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！拿酒來，酒啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.57,0:26:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒酒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.67,0:26:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.27,0:26:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.51,0:26:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨手笨腳的媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.91,0:26:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.34,0:26:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個怪裡怪氣的傢伙\N物怪看上的…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.95,0:27:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是討人厭真討人厭\N就是妳這種情緒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.05,0:27:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是討人厭真討人厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.13,0:27:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…對物怪來說\N妳非常適合他附身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.70,0:27:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好笑的！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.43,0:27:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這確實很可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.40,0:27:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.84,0:27:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這可笑之事，妳…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.08,0:27:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.54,0:27:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了多少人？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.92,0:27:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺於物怪力量的下場即是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.95,0:27:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.22,0:27:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...妳還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.03,0:27:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.00,0:27:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯就是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.07,0:27:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳每天不停仰望的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.04,0:28:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片只屬於妳的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.41,0:28:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的...天空？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.48,0:28:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.09,0:28:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.97,0:28:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.45,0:28:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳只是...看著它
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.12,0:28:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看著天空\N我就已經覺得很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.35,0:28:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...不離開這裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.29,0:28:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.96,0:28:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真正殺死的人...是誰？\N閉...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.57,0:29:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真正...殺死的人？\N閉...嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.81,0:29:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.61,0:29:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.04,0:29:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳究竟
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.78,0:29:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.98,0:29:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.15,0:29:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准再踏入蝴蝶小姐的內心！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.13,0:29:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.79,0:29:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想離開此地的話此地即是牢獄
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.43,0:29:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想留在此地的話此地即是堡壘
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.00,0:29:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡跟那裡都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.74,0:29:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一直認為此處是監牢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.48,0:29:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.75,0:29:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.69,0:29:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.73,0:30:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.30,0:30:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...為什麼不逃呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.55,0:30:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.29,0:30:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟以前的我\N簡直就是一個模子印出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.16,0:30:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這樣美麗的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.93,0:30:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能嫁入武士之家的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.37,0:30:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.40,0:30:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.77,0:30:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.54,0:30:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難纏
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.98,0:30:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...最喜歡母親大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.42,0:30:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了，蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.79,0:31:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說下去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.06,0:31:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.86,0:31:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些都是假的！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.99,0:31:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.96,0:31:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲正要上演
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.37,0:31:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.07,0:31:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二幕
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.64,0:31:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳天生就是個美人\N這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.34,0:31:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑這個臉蛋再學點技藝的話\N母親大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.85,0:31:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是出身貧寒的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.65,0:31:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能嫁入大戶人家的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.82,0:31:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.99,0:31:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔~好孩子，真是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.86,0:31:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡母親大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.86,0:31:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我希望讓她開心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.27,0:31:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一直在忍耐嗎？\N咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.37,0:31:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜犧牲自已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.64,0:31:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的...心？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.21,0:32:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說這麼多次了妳還是不懂嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.12,0:32:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.55,0:32:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兒妳不是練好幾次了？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.25,0:32:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.16,0:32:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.22,0:32:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次，從頭開始\N對不起，對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.56,0:32:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣妳怎麼嫁入武士之家？\N對不起，對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.20,0:32:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，再來一遍\N對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.54,0:32:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.55,0:32:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.23,0:32:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了！快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.27,0:32:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身已將她調教得\N不管何時都不會令家門蒙羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.04,0:33:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.68,0:33:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.14,0:33:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三幕
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.08,0:33:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後還請各位多多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.42,0:33:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.28,0:33:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把頭抬起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.69,0:33:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這樣拼命懇求
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.52,0:33:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會害我過意不去的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.69,0:33:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會茶道，彈琴跟花道是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.86,0:33:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那晚上會像蕩婦一樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.90,0:33:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦，那要看大哥怎麼調教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.47,0:33:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼\N女人只要有錢還怕找不到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.34,0:33:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後還請您多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.80,0:33:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後務必請您多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.84,0:33:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親的願望...嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.51,0:33:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N請各位務必多多照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.84,0:33:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人很早就過世了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.41,0:33:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俸祿也跟著停止
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.18,0:33:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於失去一切的母親來說
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.75,0:33:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我嫁入武士之家
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.25,0:33:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她的生存意義
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.66,0:33:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來\N我就無愧於梅澤家的代代祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.26,0:33:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.73,0:34:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以妳就成了\N替母親實現願望的工具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.77,0:34:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.14,0:34:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然那又是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.81,0:34:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.15,0:34:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.99,0:34:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.92,0:34:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了母親的願望\N而壓抑自已的心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.99,0:34:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但身為工具的妳卻...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.00,0:34:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.80,0:34:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.00,0:34:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是妳戀愛的對象...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.84,0:34:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.68,0:34:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.81,0:34:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.51,0:34:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四幕
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.28,0:34:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.02,0:34:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.52,0:34:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶也真是的\N早點拿來不就得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.69,0:35:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨手笨腳的媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.93,0:35:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼怪裡怪氣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.63,0:35:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哥哥你幹嘛娶她？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.20,0:35:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她老媽苦苦哀求我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.17,0:35:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是前一個媳婦上吊自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.51,0:35:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會讓這種女人進門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.84,0:35:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過娶來做飯剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.55,0:35:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要是也能多點情趣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.02,0:35:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭~你怎麼講這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.47,0:35:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.91,0:35:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.61,0:35:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.51,0:35:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.68,0:35:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.25,0:36:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.99,0:36:03.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.82,0:36:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.83,0:36:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...別問了...別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.93,0:36:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再問了！
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.31,0:36:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問了...別問了...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.62,0:36:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐那個面具...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.75,0:36:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並非物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.29,0:36:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是物怪操控那個戴面具的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.13,0:36:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺騙了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.10,0:36:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並把妳束縛在那個家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.97,0:36:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“真“
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.45,0:36:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.25,0:37:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而接受了母親扭曲的愛\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.22,0:37:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導致妳的心也跟著扭曲\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.72,0:37:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是被物怪纏上\N不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.16,0:37:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“理“
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.77,0:37:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...最喜歡母親大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.67,0:37:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人聽我說！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.78,0:37:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有認真練習嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.58,0:37:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要妳能嫁入豪門
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.65,0:37:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...已經很努力了\N我也會引以為傲的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.28,0:37:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很努力...很努力了\N之後再生個健康的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.75,0:37:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.75,0:37:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要我不要...\N為了得到夫家的疼愛
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.96,0:37:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要我不要啊...\N妳一定要拼個兒子出來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.16,0:37:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人聽我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.36,0:37:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好期待啊~\N母親大人妳聽我說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.74,0:38:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水天宮的符好像很有用呢\N母親大人聽我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.44,0:38:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人妳聽我說啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.24,0:38:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓他弟弟搶先的話\N那就不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.31,0:38:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人為什麼不聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.75,0:38:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說聽我說啊...\N所以妳一定要先生出小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.72,0:38:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說...\N啊~真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.76,0:38:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳聽我說好不好\N好期待哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.90,0:38:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...\N好期待哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.73,0:38:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.64,0:38:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.97,0:38:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直跟白癡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.78,0:38:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.05,0:38:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳殺掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.75,0:38:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.02,0:38:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.17,0:39:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.31,0:39:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自已？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.81,0:39:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.72,0:39:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了他人的欲望\N我殺了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.59,0:39:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記自已面貌的...\N我...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.72,0:39:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪\N殺了的人是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.12,0:39:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現出...形來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.07,0:39:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自已！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.67,0:39:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪是...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.34,0:39:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.43,0:40:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後可以問件事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.63,0:40:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無臉男為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.81,0:40:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要救我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.68,0:40:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得自已得救了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.69,0:40:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.39,0:40:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是因為...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.13,0:40:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛上妳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.00,0:40:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.94,0:40:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是個無法實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.51,0:40:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.21,0:40:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.28,0:40:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可悲的...物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.06,0:41:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.94,0:41:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝，我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.05,0:41:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫妳拿酒來在搞什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.52,0:41:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對...對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.12,0:41:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶也真是的\N早點拿來不就得了？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.82,0:41:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個笨手笨腳的媳婦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.42,0:41:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼怪裡怪氣的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.66,0:41:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那哥哥你幹嘛娶她？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.80,0:41:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她老媽苦苦哀求我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.57,0:41:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是前一個媳婦上吊自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.14,0:41:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會讓這種女人進門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.61,0:41:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過娶來做飯剛剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.38,0:41:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上要是也能多點情趣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.71,0:42:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭~你怎麼講這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.52,0:42:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.91,0:42:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳還在幹麻啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.31,0:42:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了...真是沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.45,0:42:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯\N實在是怪裡怪氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.86,0:42:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，蝴蝶\N真討人厭...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.26,0:42:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聾啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.40,0:42:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.00,0:42:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什麼事情都拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.97,0:42:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點用也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.14,0:42:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得她在想什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.24,0:43:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是怎麼教的！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.88,0:43:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶，快把酒拿來！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.01,0:43:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點拿來啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.15,0:43:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒還沒好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.35,0:43:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.96,0:43:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.16,0:43:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.91,0:43:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(完)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.95,0:43:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.59,0:43:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法笑得開懷
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.39,0:43:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.86,0:44:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.20,0:44:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能將那些無可取代的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.94,0:44:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜並活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.81,0:44:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.26,0:44:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛開在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.36,0:44:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨風緩緩飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.74,0:44:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不見的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.28,0:44:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子\N將是我此生無可比喻的珍愛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
